{"type": "article", "id": 29430, "title": "可以变成花瓶的大理石烛台", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-11T23:01:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160711180051q3k456jdrPIWTYBw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"http://katiatolstykh.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Katia Tolstykh</a> 利用黄铜和大理石设计出了一款结合烛台与花器的多功能容器 <a href=\"http://katiatolstykh.com/Octagono\" rel=\"nofollow\">Octagono</a>。极简的八边形大理石容器顶部和底部均采用了黄铜作为点缀，保证了稳定性。上方两个黄铜部件可以自由旋转，提供了额外的展示空间，不仅能够同时放置三根蜡烛，也能加入花草作为装饰，满足不同的日常需要。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711180825FJYjy4EDubrxzdAL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.003344\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711180825hGS9bQMF0YkwjxW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711180827hIXZHvkzYdJFwjn6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071118082684QUvZqXJrlPbk6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}